# Required Packages
  autoconf
  automake
  libtool
  loomlib (http://github.com/jdegges/loomlib)

# Optional Packages
  ffmpeg (swscale, avutil, avcodec)
  fftw
  freeimage
  v4l2
  
# Mac OSX Prerequisite

Add /usr/local/lib and /usr/local/include to search paths
```
$ xcode-select --install
```

# Installation

```
$ autoreconf -if
$ ./configure
$ make
$ make install
```
